      "RAM (Random Access Memory):\n1Ô∏è‚É£	It is volatile.\n2Ô∏è‚É£	It is temporary storage.\n3Ô∏è‚É£	It is expensive.\n4Ô∏è‚É£	Allows reading and writing.\n5Ô∏è‚É£	Very faster and uses more power.\n\nROM(Read Only Memory):\n1Ô∏è‚É£	It is non-volatile.\n2Ô∏è‚É£ It is permanent storage.\n3Ô∏è‚É£	It is cheap.\n4Ô∏è‚É£	Allows reading only.\n5Ô∏è‚É£	Fast and uses less power."),
